msContents.summary: Commentary in Arabic on al-ʻĀmilī's famous book on arithmetic; some Persian annotations; worm damage to the margins.

author.persName: Jawād al-Baghdādī, Jawād ibn Saʻd, -1654 or 1655
ʻĀmilī, Bahāʼ al-Dīn Muḥammad ibn Ḥusayn, 1547-1621
عاملي، بهاء الدين محمد بن حسين،

supportDesc.extent: 189 paginated leaves : 197 x 122 (165 x 85) mm, bound to 198 x 135 mm

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in naskh in black ink; pointed.

decoDesc.decoNote: Rubrications in red; overlining in black and red; numerous geometrical diagrams and several tables.

origin.p: The item is undated; probably produced in the 18th century.

history.provenance: Formerly owned by David Eugene Smith (stamp p. 374).
